      "date": "2020-08-11 21:29:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nSarah, I removed your -1 on this patch.\n\nNormally, I would have waited until Lai updated the patch, or just edited it myself to apply your cleanup.  However, but the patch is already in master-next, and there were over a hundred new patches pushed into Gerrit/Jenkins/Autotest just recently, and with the test cluster being moved I don't think this patch would finish testing before Oleg wants to land master-next tomorrow if I updated it.\n\nThere are still a number of facet_fstype() users in the test scripts, so I don't think this is a major regression to add one more.  It would have been good to clean this up before landing the patch, but I'd prefer to land it to avoid the test failure (about 1/15 of ZFS sanity test runs, which affect 1/15 of all patches).",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
